stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (WHY TODDLERS HAVE TANTRUMS \(It's Normal!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Tantrums are NOT bad behavior. They're a sign your child's brain is overwhelmed and they) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (haven't yet developed the skills to regulate emotions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 652.2 Td (BRAIN SCIENCE: The prefrontal cortex \(logic, self-control\) isn't fully developed until age) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (25. Toddlers are literally unable to 'calm down on command.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.4 Td (YOUR JOB: Be the calm in their storm. Co-regulate \(stay calm yourself\) and they will learn) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600.4 Td (to self-regulate over time.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
