10 0 obj
<< /Length 894 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (THE P.A.U.S.E. METHOD) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (When a tantrum starts, use this 5-step framework:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (P - PAUSE. Stop what you're doing. Take 3 breaths.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 652.2 Td (A - ACKNOWLEDGE. 'I see you're really upset right now.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (U - UNDERSTAND. What need is unmet? \(hungry? tired? overwhelmed?\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (S - SUPPORT. Offer connection: 'I'm here. Would you like a hug?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.2 Td (E - EMPATHIZE. 'It's hard when we can't have what we want.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 586.4 Td (AFTER the storm passes:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 572.4 Td (1. Validate: 'You had really big feelings.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 558.4 Td (2. Name it: 'That was frustration/anger/sadness.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.4 Td (3. Problem-solve: 'Next time, you can...') Tj ET
endstream
endobj
