12 0 obj
<< /Length 1172 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (SCRIPTS: WHAT TO SAY \(20 Common Situations\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (When: They can't have something) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (Say: "I hear you. You really want that. It's okay to feel disappointed. The answer is) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (still no, AND I love you.") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 618.4 Td (When: They hit/bite/throw) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (Say: "I won't let you hurt. Hitting hurts. You can stomp your feet or squeeze this pillow) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (instead.") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 560.6 Td (When: They won't leave the park) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.6 Td (Say: "We're leaving in 5 minutes. Would you like to go down the slide one more time or) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (swing?") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 502.8 Td (When: They won't share) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 486.8 Td (Say: "It's hard to share. You can have it for 2 more minutes, then it's your friend's) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 472.8 Td (turn.") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 445.0 Td (When: They want YOU to do it) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 429.0 Td (Say: "You want help. I'll help you start, then you can finish. I believe you can do it.") Tj ET
endstream
endobj
