14 0 obj
<< /Length 1129 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (SCRIPTS \(continued\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (When: They're frustrated \(can't do something\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (Say: "That IS frustrating! Would you like to try again, or take a break and come back?") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 632.4 Td (When: They say 'I HATE YOU') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 616.4 Td (Say: "I can see you're really angry. It's okay to be angry. I love you even when you're) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (mad.") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 574.6 Td (When: They won't get dressed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 558.6 Td (Say: "It's time to get dressed. Would you like the blue shirt or the red shirt? You) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.6 Td (choose!") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 516.8 Td (When: They melt down at bedtime) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 500.8 Td (Say: "Your body is tired even if your brain doesn't think so. Let's do our calm-down) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 486.8 Td (routine together.") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 459.0 Td (When: Public tantrum \(store/restaurant\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 443.0 Td (Say: "I see you're having a hard time. Let's step outside for a minute to feel better.") Tj ET
endstream
endobj
