BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (TANTRUM PREVENTION CHECKLIST) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Most tantrums are PREVENTABLE. Daily check:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (  [ ] Fed regularly \(no more than 3 hours between food\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 652.2 Td (  [ ] Slept enough \(age-appropriate nap + bedtime\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (  [ ] Given choices throughout the day \(autonomy!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (  [ ] Warned before transitions \('5 more minutes, then...'\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.2 Td (  [ ] Had 1-on-1 connection time with parent today) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.2 Td (  [ ] Physical activity/outdoor play today) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.2 Td (  [ ] Not overscheduled \(downtime is essential!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.2 Td (  [ ] Routines are predictable and consistent) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.4 Td (If 3+ are unchecked: a meltdown is LIKELY coming. Address the need!) Tj ET
